📍 S A V A N N A H  S T A Y S 🏡 I’m so excited to debut the long-awaited and frequently-asked Savannah apartment rental tour! I have stayed with various rental companies, Airbnbs, and hotels when visiting Savannah and this time I got to stay in a @savannahstays apartment, hosted and designed by the fabulous @farrellclick! 

This apartment is Savannah Stays’ “Square 12” and is one of the most stunning rental spaces I’ve ever seen. Everything about it, including the details, the bonus treats, the king bed, the location, and all-you-can-think-of amenities, was perfect. Savannah Stays rentals are also centrally located in downtown Savannah and steps from your favorite spots, and coming home to special touches such as a rocking chair deck and @haleteaco tea after a day of exploring was a dream. To say I had a relaxing birthday weekend is an understatement! 

A huge thanks to Farrell and @savannahstays for a wonderful time - and I can now strongly recommend staying with them on your next trip! Not only do they have short and long-term apartment rentals, but they are also debuting airbnbs with the same vibe✨

PS: the Savannah Stays team are good friends and they graciously let me stay as a personal gift - this is not paid content and just me spreading the word 🤍

Stunning 37th Street Historic Charmer! Luxurious modern details with original 1950’s character restored. The lush, landscaped exterior will welcome you from the start. The stunning front porch is perfect for enjoying that morning cup of coffee while overlooking one of Savannah’s most iconic Streets. Original hardwoods have been restored throughout the living space. The copious number of windows allow light to flood throughout the home. Brand new Kitchen with custom cabinetry, honed Calcutta marble counters and new Samsung Bespoke White Glass appliances. Cozy living room leads to a large dining room off the kitchen. Through the backdoor is the real star of this home, a private courtyard. This open space provides natural sunlight and air without compromising privacy. The ample sunlight is perfect for the avid gardener or urban farmer. The centerpiece is the custom wood burning fireplace to enjoy the cooler Savannah evenings. Corner lot with a one car garage to finish off this home.

Perfectly positioned near Thomas Square / Streetcar District, Starland, Historic Downtown Savannah with some of Savannah’s best new spots just a short walk away- Perc Coffee, Brochus, Shuk, Hop Atomica, Cotton and Rye, , Starland Yard, Green Truck Pub.

Experience the epitome of Southern living on Savannah’s iconic 37th st.  A historic gem nestled among Savannah’s oaks and Spanish moss.   This charming two-story home, dating back to 1914, has been thoughtfully renovated with attention to detail and tasteful designer touches, creating a harmonious blend of historic charm & modern sophistication. 
As you step inside, you are greeted with almost 10 ft ceilings and an array of original details that have been lovingly preserved.  From the elegant wood floors, large windows for infinite natural light, and FOUR stunning original mantes, every corner exudes a timeless allure.  On the first floor you’ll find fully functional galley kitchen, bedroom and fully bath.  Upstairs boasts a bathroom with a gorgeous clawfoot cast iron tub, mosaic tile flooring and 3 additional bedrooms with original wood flooring.
Perfectly positioned near Thomas Square / Streetcar District, Starland, Historic Downtown Savannah with some of Savannah’s best new spots just a short walk away- Perc Coffee, Brochus, Shuk, Hop Atomica, Cotton and Rye, , Starland Yard, Green Truck Pub.
